annotationA: Retina aberrant in pattern (Rap) binds to the Anaphase-Promoting Complex/Cyclosome (APC/C) ubiquitin ligase to stimulate its activity during G1 phase
annotationB: Anaphase promoting complex subunit 4, isoform A; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of mitotic metaphase/anaphase transition; anaphase-promoting complex-dependent proteasomal ubiquitin-dependent protein catabolic process
